[Detail]
**核心文件路径**:

| 文件 | 大小 | 职责 |
|------|------|------|
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py` | 38.8KB | Agent 构建入口（830行） |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/backends/protocol.py` | 26KB | 后端协议定义 |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/backends/composite.py` | 28.9KB | 组合后端实现 |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/middleware/filesystem.py` | 90.4KB | 文件操作中间件 |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/middleware/summarization.py` | 64.9KB | 摘要压缩中间件 |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/middleware/skills.py` | 39.1KB | 技能加载中间件 |
| `libs/deepagents/deepagents/middleware/subagents.py` | 33.8KB | 子智能体中间件 |
| `libs/acp/deepagents_acp/server.py` | 42.1KB | ACP 协议服务器 |

**关键类/函数**:

| 符号 | 位置 | 作用 |
|------|------|------|
| `create_deep_agent()` | graph.py:217 | 主入口 API |
| `DeepAgentState` | graph.py:63 | 状态定义 |
| `BackendProtocol` | backends/protocol.py | 后端接口 |
| `FilesystemMiddleware` | middleware/filesystem.py | 文件工具 |
| `SubAgentMiddleware` | middleware/subagents.py | 子任务 |
| `HarnessProfile` | profiles/harness/ | 行为配置 |
| `resolve_model()` | _models.py | 模型解析 |

**配置文件**:

| 文件 | 作用 |
|------|------|
| `pyproject.toml` | 包元数据、依赖、工具配置 |
| `release-please-config.json` | 发布配置 |
| `.release-please-manifest.json` | 版本追踪 |
| `.pre-commit-config.yaml` | 提交钩子 |
| `.github/workflows/ci.yml` | CI 管线 |

